'''一氧化钴'''（CoO）是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，以灰黑色的[[氧化物|氧化物]]粉末或橄榄绿到红色晶体存在。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://msds.chem.ox.ac.uk/CO/cobalt_oxide.html |title=Safety (MSDS) data for cobalt oxide |publisher=The Physical and Theoretical Chemistry Laboratory, Oxford University |accessdate=2008-11-11 |archive-date=2010-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028054849/http://msds.chem.ox.ac.uk/CO/cobalt_oxide.html }}</ref> 它在[[陶瓷|陶瓷]]工业中被广泛用作添加剂，以制造蓝色釉料和搪瓷。氧化亚钴在化学工业中用于生产钴(II)盐。

== 结构和性质 ==
CoO 晶体是[[岩盐|岩盐]]结构，晶格常数为 4.2615 Å。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.35.6847|title=Percolation effects and magnetic properties of the randomly diluted fcc system CopMg1-pO|year=1987|author1=Kannan, R. |author2=Seehra, Mohindar S. |journal=Physical Review B|volume=35|pages=6847–6853|issue=13}}</ref>

它在16 °C下是[[反铁磁性|反铁磁性]]的。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.24.419|title=Principal magnetic susceptibilities and uniaxial stress experiments in CoO|year=1981|author1=Silinsky, P. S. |author2=Seehra, Mohindar S. |journal=Physical Review B|volume=24|pages=419–423}}</ref> 
== 製備 ==

一氧化鈷可藉由將[[四氧化三鈷|四氧化三鈷]]加熱至950℃時製得：<ref>Process for making a cobalt oxide catalyst, James, Leonard E. (Richmond, VA) Crescentini, Lamberto (Chester, VA) 
Fisher, William B. (Chester, VA) 1983. http://www.freepatentsonline.com/4389339.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.freepatentsonline.com/4389339.html |date=20110615022944 }}</ref>
2 Co<sub>3</sub>O<sub>4</sub> → 6 CoO + O<sub>2</sub>

尽管可商购获得，但一氧化钴可以在实验室中通过电解氯化亚钴溶液来制备。 <ref>{{cite journal|author=Kern, S.|journal= J. Chem. Soc.|year= 1876|page=880|doi=10.1039/JS8762900876|volume=29|title=Inorganic chemistry|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-the-chemical-society_1876_29/page/880}}</ref>

CoCl<sub>2</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O → CoO + H<sub>2</sub> + Cl<sub>2</sub>

一氧化钴也可以通过沉淀[[氢氧化钴|氢氧化钴]]，然后进行热脱水来制备：

: CoX<sub>2</sub> + 2 KOH → Co(OH)<sub>2</sub> + 2 KX
: Co(OH)<sub>2</sub> → CoO + H<sub>2</sub>O

